ygData.messageBody:
well hello Dewayne, good to meet you, my name is Jose and i play
Redspider a lvl 22 rogue on bristle bane, there is not too much action
that goes on on this list but every now and then we do get some good
information going on between us (there is even a Guide among us) so we
get some real good information on how to go about dealing with the gms,
i am not much of a story writer myself but i will cheack in every now
and then on your list, sounds like a lot of fun

Dewayne wrote:
>
> Hello everyone, nice to meet you! I've been playing EQ for awhile now and its nice to join a list dedicated to us gay players :-) My name is Dewayne and I play on the Innoruuk server. My primary character is 30th lvl druid named Khaav, but I have a lvl 13 twink enchanter named Maharet. Feel free to give me a /tell if you play on Innoruuk. I'm not exactly open there but not exactly closeted, some of my guild and a few hunting buddies know.
>
> Also, I just started a new email list for gay eq players, one that I want to be primarily a roleplaying list. RP stories are encouraged. Steamy stuff is allowed but no porn. To join, go to http://www.egroups.com/group/EQ_Gays . I look forward to chatting on both of these lists :-)
>
> Khaav Sundropped
